    "description": "Ginnung is a tight platformer with simple and versatile movement for you to master. Perfect your escape in 50+ levels, and slay the monsters in your way! Set in a mysterious world of Norse spirits and Gods.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125270/extras/568516678fe1aa5c8d5a7e6d531393e1.webp?t=1670433350\" width=208 height=60 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>Ginnung is a movement focused platformer with speed and tight controls. Run, wall jump and dash your way with speed, whilst fighting the monsters that await you. This world is not where you belong. Master the levels and movement to ultimatly escape your Ginnung with style!<br><br><br>You can dash in any direction and will reset upon touching a wall or the ground. Gain extra dashes by bouncing off any projectiles. You can also dash towards the ground to gain a small speed boost, which will grant higher jump. Use this to find secret routes and collectibles hidden in the levels. <br><br>You are hunted by the spirits of this world. Use your trusty weapon to slay all that is in your way. Including a refletion of yourself, which you will battle in intense boss fights.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Last stand</h2>If you are slain, you will enter Last stand. A second chance to complete the level. A death timer will count down if you are touching the ground. Try and stay airborne as long as possible to clutch up.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2125270/extras/4d0c3ab8d94a0009425c7110f5ca4b85.webp?t=1670433350\" width=160 height=60 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>60 Levels<br></li><li>Versatile and fast movement<br></li><li>Battle spirits in boss fights<br></li><li>Secret retro themed levels<br></li><li>Many secrets to find<br></li><li>Handcrafted levels for you to perfect<br></li><li>Controller support</li></ul>",
